-- U.K. Proposes Eight More Sites as Suitable to Build Nuclear-Energy Plants
-- B y   C a t h e r i n e   A i r l i e
-- 2010-10-18T10:01:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-18/u-k-proposes-eight-more-sites-as-suitable-to-build-nuclear-energy-plants.html
The U.K. listed eight sites as
“potentially suitable” for new nuclear power by 2025, and
ruled out three others in an assessment of energy needs
published today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
